ygData.messageBody:
Greetings!

I'd like to remind everyone that if you have some new information regarding
diamond dust (such as the Crushed Dufrenite search), please pass it along
and I'll include it in the already growing section of the Compendium. (Be
sure to check it out if you haven't already).

As far as the OOT search goes, if you are all serious about it then I would
be willing to start another page on the Compendium dedicated to the search
of the downed ship. Please write in stating where you have already searched,
preferablly including zone coordinates. I'll then put a map of the zone up
indicating what has already been covered.

--------------
